{"tid":531552,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"cpu壞咗:( 可以點做","createTime":"2018-01-17T03:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T09:04:05.000Z","uid":126480,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eae2049abd89b7e040b62325bd0c4f448221e9b3","tid":531552,"uid":126480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"琴日打打下機撞到部電腦<br />\n突然就無咗反應<br />\n重開咗幾次電腦個MON都係一直no video input<br />\n打開機箱見到老母板個EZ debug led粒cpu燈着咗<br />\n開機制塊板無燈同淨係㩒到一次開機<br />\n已經試過將所有野拆出黎再重新裝一次都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪粒cpu燒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ncpu:AMD R5 1400 <br />\n老母板:MSI B350M gaming pro<br />\n顯卡顯你老母:MSI GTX 1050ti"},{"pid":"cc3e1ee30c64914997c1fc58afbfaf6a064838a3","tid":531552,"uid":67792,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"返5p"},{"pid":"281057da2f27d60d03b19ab1a2c6d6decd2fe5cf","tid":531552,"uid":126480,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"部機係自己砌既<br />\n一開始砌完部機都係咁<br />\n個時係裝cpu拆出黎再裝一次就搞掂<br />\n但今次無咁好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋今次拆cpu既時候發現粒u既邊邊位有啲灰黑色既膠擠咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前新裝既時候係無架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb15232f6989939150d2a816a5f0861231572f1","tid":531552,"uid":23815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"281057da2f27d60d03b19ab1a2c6d6decd2fe5cf","tid":531552,"uid":126480,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"部機係自己砌既<br />\n一開始砌完部機都係咁<br />\n個時係裝cpu拆出黎再裝一次就搞掂<br />\n但今次無咁好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" clas